projectDetails.title: Personal Portfolio Website
projectDetails.description: A personal portfolio website to showcase my projects and skills. Built using React for the frontend and Node.js with Express for the backend. The website features a responsive design, interactive elements, and a contact form that sends messages directly to my email.

projectDetails.title: Spec-Generator
projectDetails.description: A web application that generates LS-G codes autonomously based on user inputs. The frontend is built with React, providing a user-friendly interface, while the backend utilizes Node.js and Express to handle code generation logic and data processing. The application also integrates PostgreSQL for storing user data and generated codes.

projectDetails.title: Regression Analysis Machine Learning with Python
projectDetails.description: Developed a regression analysis project utilizing key concepts in Python, including NumPy and Pandas. Utilized machine learning techniques to perform regression analysis on a dataset, extracting insights and making predictions based on the data.

projectDetails.title: Designed a Butterworth Filter
projectDetails.description: Designed a Butterworth filter signal in digital Signal Processing to generate output by taking user inputs Using python
